---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// SEO metadata
const title = "Data Deletion Instructions - NeuDayAI | How to Delete Your Data";
const description = "Learn how to request deletion of your personal data from NeuDayAI affiliated apps and services. Comprehensive instructions for data removal and privacy rights.";
const keywords = ["Data Deletion", "Delete Personal Data", "Privacy Rights", "NeuDayAI Data Removal", "GDPR Right to Erasure", "Data Protection", "Account Deletion"];
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
  pageType="article"
>
  <main class="pt-32">
    <section class="py-20" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8" itemprop="headline">Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
        
        <div class="prose lg:prose-lg" itemprop="mainContentOfPage">
          <p>Effective Date: June 5, 2024</p>
          
          <p>At NeuDayAI Technologies Pvt. Ltd., we respect your privacy and your right to control your personal data. This page provides comprehensive instructions on how to request the deletion of your data associated with any NeuDayAI-affiliated applications and services.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Your Right to Data Deletion</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-700">Under various privacy laws including GDPR, CCPA, and other applicable regulations, you have the right to request the deletion of your personal data. We are committed to honoring these requests promptly and transparently.</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Deletion for Meta (Facebook) Connected Apps</h2>
          
          <p>If you accessed our services through your Facebook account or any Meta platform integration:</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">Step-by-Step Process:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Visit Facebook App Settings:</strong> Navigate to your <a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings?tab=applications" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">Facebook App Settings Page</a></li>
            <li><strong>Locate NeuDayAI App:</strong> Find any NeuDayAI-affiliated application in your list of connected apps and websites</li>
            <li><strong>Remove Application:</strong> Click "Remove" or "Revoke Access" to disconnect the app from your Facebook account</li>
            <li><strong>Confirm Removal:</strong> Follow the confirmation prompts to complete the disconnection process</li>
          </ol>
          
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <p class="text-green-800"><strong>Automatic Data Deletion:</strong> Upon removal, all personal data, access tokens, and associated information related to your Facebook account will be permanently erased from our systems within <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Direct Data Deletion Request</h2>
          
          <p>For comprehensive data deletion or if you accessed our services through other means, you can submit a direct deletion request:</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">Email Request Process:</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
            <p><strong>Email Address:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@neudayai.com?subject=Data%20Deletion%20Request" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">contact@neudayai.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Subject Line:</strong> "Data Deletion Request"</p>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">Required Information:</h3>
          <p>To process your deletion request efficiently, please include the following details in your email:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Platform/App Name:</strong> Specify which NeuDayAI application or service you used</li>
            <li><strong>Account Identifier:</strong> Your registered email address, username, or user ID</li>
            <li><strong>Registration Date:</strong> Approximate date when you created your account (if known)</li>
            <li><strong>Platform Source:</strong> How you accessed our service (App Store, Play Store, Web, Meta, etc.)</li>
            <li><strong>Additional Context:</strong> Any specific data categories you're particularly concerned about</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Deletion Timeline and Process</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">Processing Timeline:</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
              <div>
                <p><strong>Request Acknowledgment:</strong> We will confirm receipt of your request within <strong>48 hours</strong></p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
              <div>
                <p><strong>Identity Verification:</strong> We may request additional information to verify your identity (2-5 business days)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
              <div>
                <p><strong>Data Deletion:</strong> Complete removal of your data from our active systems (within 30 days)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">âœ“</div>
              <div>
                <p><strong>Confirmation:</strong> Email confirmation once deletion is complete</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">What Data Will Be Deleted:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone number)</li>
            <li>Account credentials and authentication tokens</li>
            <li>Usage data and activity logs</li>
            <li>Preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Communication history with our support team</li>
            <li>Analytics and behavioral data</li>
            <li>Any uploaded or generated content</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention Exceptions</h2>
          
          <p>Please note that certain data may be retained for legitimate business purposes or legal compliance:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> Data required for tax, audit, or regulatory compliance</li>
            <li><strong>Security Records:</strong> Anonymized security logs for fraud prevention</li>
            <li><strong>Aggregated Analytics:</strong> De-identified data used for product improvement</li>
            <li><strong>Backup Systems:</strong> Data in backup systems will be deleted during the next scheduled purge cycle</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          
          <p>If you used third-party authentication services (Google, Apple, Microsoft) to access our apps, you may also need to:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Revoke app permissions in your respective third-party account settings</li>
            <li>Review and manage connected applications in your Google, Apple, or Microsoft accounts</li>
            <li>Contact the respective third-party providers for their data deletion processes</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Verification and Security</h2>
          
          <p>To protect your privacy and prevent unauthorized deletion requests, we may:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Request additional verification of your identity</li>
            <li>Ask you to confirm the deletion request from your registered email address</li>
            <li>Require answers to security questions if available</li>
            <li>Request proof of account ownership through previous interactions</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Post-Deletion Access</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-700">Once your data is deleted, you will no longer be able to access your account or any associated services. This action is <strong>irreversible</strong>. Please ensure you have downloaded any important data before submitting your deletion request.</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">8. Alternative Options</h2>
          
          <p>Before proceeding with complete data deletion, consider these alternatives:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Account Deactivation:</strong> Temporarily disable your account while retaining data</li>
            <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> Request a copy of your data before deletion</li>
            <li><strong>Selective Deletion:</strong> Delete specific data categories while maintaining account access</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy Settings:</strong> Adjust privacy settings to limit data collection</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
          
          <p>For any questions, concerns, or assistance with your data deletion request, please contact us:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>NeuDayAI Technologies Pvt. Ltd.</strong></p>
            <p class="mb-2">604, Solitaire Paradise,<br>Pink City Road, Wakad,<br>Pune, India, 411057</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@neudayai.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">contact@neudayai.com</a></p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Privacy Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@neudayai.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">privacy@neudayai.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+918983142496" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">+91 8983142496</a></p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">10. Updates to These Instructions</h2>
          
          <p>We may update these data deletion instructions from time to time to reflect changes in our processes or legal requirements. Any updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date. We encourage you to review these instructions periodically.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500 mt-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Need Help?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-700">If you encounter any difficulties or have questions about the data deletion process, our privacy team is here to help. Don't hesitate to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:privacy@neudayai.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">privacy@neudayai.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "speakable": {
        "@type": "SpeakableSpecification",
        "cssSelector": ["h1", "h2", "h3"]
      },
      "name": "Data Deletion Instructions - NeuDayAI",
      "description": "Learn how to request deletion of your personal data from NeuDayAI affiliated apps and services.",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "NeuDayAI",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://www.neudayai.com/images/logo-horizontal-light.svg"
        }
      },
      "breadcrumb": {
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 1,
            "name": "Home",
            "item": "https://www.neudayai.com"
          },
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 2,
            "name": "Data Deletion Instructions",
            "item": "https://www.neudayai.com/data-deletion"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
